items.title: Tamil Nadu CM Stalin discusses India re-entry with Ford Motors
items.description: Ford Motors' Chennai plant remains shut after it the exited India in 2021. Stalin says the two sides are exploring the possibility of 'make in Tamil Nadu for the world'
